{"tid":2210002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾祖康：若12港人是在香港水域被綁架","createTime":"2020-09-20T05:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T06:35:56.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f8163f00b87d732684360a5fc7b99bae55f1da97","tid":2210002,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/C-GUI-200225-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FC-GUI-200225-11.jpg&h=e8536612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joe.chung.547/posts/3725540450789901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoe.chung.547%2Fposts%2F3725540450789901&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=c6736c6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joe.chung.547/posts/3725540450789901</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：鍾祖康<br />\n<br />\n在郭卓堅冒死揭發下，幾乎已可肯定，中國海警是在香港水警配合下，闖入香港水域綁架了12名香港人，而此事不難從多方的定位數據予以求證。因此，我非常相信，除非中短期內中國軍事上遭受美國重創之類的事發生，習近平絕不可能會讓這批人在十年八載之間活著出來揭露真相，這批人未來十年八載的日子，估計慘過死刑，當中即使有提前釋放的，也必會確保要像潑墨女子董瑤瓊那樣變成癡呆、喪失與人溝通能力後才有機會。香港人和香港的意見領袖對待此事看來是過於輕率了。"},{"pid":"264c1a9e7f977cf73775f4f420a1dcd7d1323a9f","tid":2210002,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"841c52a5fd9de2d67c528d38707012478ff323bc","tid":2210002,"uid":18995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:48:49.000Z","msg":"有睇過高佬廷同涂謹申搶Owen光環/功勞開記者會就知咩事<br />\n班泛狗只係擔功勞呃票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d7d854ab37680e6a49f219ba525ab1a6961132","tid":2210002,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"9up幾句就叫冒死告發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a56c66aa37d72f717de3cb9f2c316d0a930d1b","tid":2210002,"uid":192296,"like":0,"disli